			<h3 ><a href="#p4289" rel="nofollow"><!-- google_ad_section_start -->Re: O's MUST sign Yu Darvish<!-- google_ad_section_end --></a></h3>
			<p class="author"><!-- google_ad_section_start(weight=ignore) --><a rel="nofollow" href="./viewtopic.php?p=4289&amp;sid=af14f791c0debbe76d2339c2a0fe3670#p4289"><img src="./styles/static/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="11" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a>Post <a href="./viewtopic.php?p=4289&amp;sid=af14f791c0debbe76d2339c2a0fe3670#p4289" onclick="prompt('Direct link to post:',this.href); return false;"><strong>#11</strong></a>&nbsp;by <strong><a href="./memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=89&amp;sid=af14f791c0debbe76d2339c2a0fe3670" style="color: #000000;" class="username-coloured">Don</a></strong> &raquo; October 18th, 2011, 10:53 am <!-- google_ad_section_end --></p>

			

			<div id="explanation4289" style="display:none" >
